  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/e569fed1826a03bfb805434d32f749e5.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><br>Sometime at the end of the last century near the withered town of Lingyi, dusk fell upon the electric gates of the Junior High. A passionate girl who could never become a black sheep opened her hands and embraced the earth.<br>Her dear friend Li Xiangfan, someone who once knew everything, had not a single word to say.<br><br><br><strong>\"\"Hush, don't speak of the black sheep, its instinct is to live amongst the flock.\"。\"</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2acd4010dadeb4c04d59a7708923697d.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2acd4010dadeb4c04d59a7708923697d.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2acd4010dadeb4c04d59a7708923697d.mp4?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>· Moderate elements of psychological horror, integrated into urban legends within a school setting.<br>· Collect information left amongst the ruins and uncover the truth behind the year's events.<br>· Beware of monsters born out of malice, and discover their true identities.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/be0829bb3161f4c23598459ef95d931c.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/be0829bb3161f4c23598459ef95d931c.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/be0829bb3161f4c23598459ef95d931c.mp4?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>· The game consists of five chapters, with each chapter corresponding to a series of events that happened in the past year, with the player acts as a bystander in these events. As you watch on from the sidelines, how you choose to save the black sheep is up to you.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/212fc59a0ba5b24b0764be805ae2cbe9.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/212fc59a0ba5b24b0764be805ae2cbe9.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/212fc59a0ba5b24b0764be805ae2cbe9.mp4?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>· This is a story-driven adventure game, where even things that seem simple at first may be difficult to pin down... Players must search for the truth by gathering opinions, changing their perspective, and assuming different identities until the butcher in the flock is found.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2e2447fb7a9ad8942099dd617aef0c16.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=355 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2e2447fb7a9ad8942099dd617aef0c16.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/e569fed1826a03bfb805434d32f749e5.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 /></span><br><br>Sometime at the end of the last century near the withered town of Lingyi, dusk fell upon the electric gates of the Junior High. A passionate girl who could never become a black sheep opened her hands and embraced the earth.<br>Her dear friend Li Xiangfan, someone who once knew everything, had not a single word to say.<br><br><br><strong>\"\"Hush, don't speak of the black sheep, its instinct is to live amongst the flock.\"。\"</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2acd4010dadeb4c04d59a7708923697d.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2acd4010dadeb4c04d59a7708923697d.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2acd4010dadeb4c04d59a7708923697d.mp4?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>· Moderate elements of psychological horror, integrated into urban legends within a school setting.<br>· Collect information left amongst the ruins and uncover the truth behind the year's events.<br>· Beware of monsters born out of malice, and discover their true identities.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/be0829bb3161f4c23598459ef95d931c.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/be0829bb3161f4c23598459ef95d931c.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/be0829bb3161f4c23598459ef95d931c.mp4?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>· The game consists of five chapters, with each chapter corresponding to a series of events that happened in the past year, with the player acts as a bystander in these events. As you watch on from the sidelines, how you choose to save the black sheep is up to you.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/212fc59a0ba5b24b0764be805ae2cbe9.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/212fc59a0ba5b24b0764be805ae2cbe9.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/212fc59a0ba5b24b0764be805ae2cbe9.mp4?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>· This is a story-driven adventure game, where even things that seem simple at first may be difficult to pin down... Players must search for the truth by gathering opinions, changing their perspective, and assuming different identities until the butcher in the flock is found.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2e2447fb7a9ad8942099dd617aef0c16.poster.avif?t=1745567208\" width=630 height=355 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682260/extras/2e2447fb7a9ad8942099dd617aef0c16.webm?t=1745567208\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
